 - added logo-pictures before introduction 
 - added 4 bit native screen support with monitor support (PAL/NTSC/DBLPAL/DBLNTSC)
   and CGX support
 - added double buffer and change palettes in right moment
 - added harddisk music playback
 - added joystick support
 - slower closing credits
 - memory and speed optimizations
 - GUI for settings
 - icons
